---
import Layout from 'src/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About DocForge AI - Our Story">

	<main>
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-800 py-16 lg:py-24">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="text-center">
					<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
						About DocForge AI
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						We're on a mission to transform how developers understand and maintain code through AI-powered documentation.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Story Section -->
		<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
						DocForge AI was born from a simple observation: developers spend countless hours trying to understand existing codebases, whether they're joining a new team, maintaining legacy systems, or returning to their own code months later.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
						Traditional documentation often falls shortâ€”it's either outdated, incomplete, or simply doesn't exist. We realized that with the advent of advanced language models like Claude and Gemini, we could solve this problem once and for all.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
						Our platform doesn't just parse codeâ€”it understands it. By combining cutting-edge AI with vector embeddings and semantic search, we create documentation that's comprehensive, searchable, and actually useful.
					</p>

					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">The Problem We Solve</h2>
					<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
						<ul class="space-y-4">
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">70% of developers</strong>
									<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Say understanding existing code is their biggest challenge</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">40+ hours per month</strong>
									<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Average time spent deciphering undocumented code</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">$85 billion annually</strong>
									<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Lost productivity due to poor documentation</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">Our Approach</h2>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
								<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">AI Understanding</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Not just parsing, but truly understanding code logic and intent</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
								<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Comprehensive Docs</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">From high-level architecture to detailed method descriptions</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
								<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Intelligent Search</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Vector embeddings enable semantic search across your entire codebase</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">Our Values</h2>
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 flex items-center">
								<span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mr-3">ðŸŽ¯</span>
								Developer-First
							</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
								Every feature we build starts with developer needs. We're developers ourselves, and we understand the pain of working with undocumented code.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 flex items-center">
								<span class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mr-3">ðŸ”’</span>
								Security & Privacy
							</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
								Your code is your intellectual property. We never train our models on your data, and we're SOC 2 compliant with end-to-end encryption.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 flex items-center">
								<span class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mr-3">ðŸš€</span>
								Continuous Innovation
							</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
								As AI technology evolves, so do we. We're constantly improving our models and adding new features to make documentation even better.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">The Team</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
						DocForge AI is built by a team of engineers, researchers, and designers who've experienced the documentation problem firsthand. We come from companies like Google, Microsoft, and Amazon, where we've seen how poor documentation can slow down even the best teams.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
						Our diverse backgrounds in machine learning, software engineering, and user experience design come together to create a product that's not just powerful, but also intuitive and enjoyable to use.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA Section -->
		<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
					Join Us in Revolutionizing Code Documentation
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
					Start your journey towards better documentation today.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="/demo" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-blue-600 text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl font-semibold">
						Try DocForge AI Free
					</a>
					<a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-4 bg-transparent text-white text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border-2 border-white">
						Get in Touch
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 py-12">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
				<p>&copy; 2025 DocForge AI. All rights reserved.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>